casebody.data:
Jermaine O'Neal WALKER
v.
CLERK OF SUPERIOR COURT GUILFORD COUNTY. No. 340P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 30, 2005. Jermaine O'Neal Walker, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 21st day of June 2005 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Guilford County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in Conference this the 30th day of June 2005."
